d canvas our point of view innovators not innovations our way of working real world projects radical collaboration learning experiences take a d school class use our methods attend executive education be a project partner get a degree browse our reading list the latest d news blog social entrepreneurship k 12 education press about us our team tours faqs getting to our building contact us d school d school d school institute of design at stanford d canvas dschool january 29 2012 www dcanvas org d canvas is an online collaboration tool that captures the design thinking process in a dynamic and shareable way it provides a digital canvas to visually capture and build upon the ideas insights photos and videos generated in each phase users can dynamically move tag and organize content to iterate and refine the problem statement whether you re a novice or an experienced design thinker d canvas guides and inspires users through toolkits and tutorial videos to achieve greater depth of practice it enables online collaboration as well as public sharing with the ability to follow other challenges and interest areas around the world it is a virtual representation of the design thinking process in action and fosters a connected and engaged global learning community of design thinkers team josh schwartzman poyi chen katie johnson dianna kane posted in hack d tagged project leave a reply click here to cancel reply name email website comment notify me of follow up comments by email notify me of new posts by email 2012 stanford university institute of design all rights reserved terms of use copyright complaints internal login
